## 5. raw#10 honest C3

1. **177Lu-PSMA-617 Pluvicto 2022** = first FDA-approved PSMA radioligand for mCRPC. Novartis VISION trial demonstrated rPFS + OS benefit. β-emitter (Lu-177 6.7d half-life, max 0.5 MeV β, soft tissue range 1-2 mm). companion DX = 68Ga-PSMA-11 / 18F-DCFPyL PET. quantum-VQE 의 chelator (DOTA) + radionuclide + PSMA receptor stack 적합.
2. **177Lu-DOTATATE Lutathera 2018** = first FDA PRRT (peptide receptor radionuclide therapy). GEP-NET 적응증. NETTER-1 trial. Novartis 2018 Advanced Accelerator Applications 인수. companion DX = 68Ga-DOTATATE Netspot 2016. SSTR2 targeting.
3. **223Ra-dichloride Xofigo 2013** = first α-emitter therapeutic FDA. bone metastasis CRPC. Ra-223 11.4d half-life, 4 α decay chain. ALSYMPCA trial. Bayer. mineral-mimicking bone-seeking (calcium analog). 본 entry palliative_care 와 cross-link.
4. **PSMA + SSTR + FAP + GRPR pipeline 폭발 2020-2024** = theranostic 의 paradigm shift (radioligand pharma + nuclear medicine convergence). Novartis (Pluvicto + Lutathera) + Bayer (Xofigo + Th-227) + Lantheus (Pylarify) + POINT/Telix/Curium 등 신생.
5. **18F-FDG (1976+) + 99mTc-Tc 일반 SPECT (1970+)** = theranostic 의 imaging foundation. universal cancer staging + cardiology + neurology classical 핵의학.
6. **amyloid PET 3 (florbetapir 2012 + florbetaben 2014 + flutemetamol 2013) + tau PET (flortaucipir 2020)** = Alzheimer DX 핵의학 paradigm. cross-link `.roadmap.disease_neurodegen` lecanemab 2023 + donanemab 2024 disease-modifying mAb 와 동기화.
7. **123I-ioflupane DaTscan 2011** = Parkinson DAT 영상. cross-link `.roadmap.disease_neurodegen`. classical SPECT.
8. **Ac-225 + Th-227 + Pb-212 next-gen α-emitter pipeline** = β-emitter (Lu-177) 의 cross-fire range 한계 + α-emitter 의 high LET (Linear Energy Transfer) + short range advantage. 225Ac-PSMA-617 mCRPC trial 진행 중. supply chain (Ac-225 producer 부족) bottleneck 가 commercial 한계.
9. **immuno-PET 89Zr-mAb research** = pembrolizumab/trastuzumab 의 biodistribution + tumor uptake 영상화. companion DX 가 ICI/ADC 의 patient selection 신 paradigm pipeline.
10. **wet-lab + clinical RCT 없음** — quantum-only in-silico, theranostic 임상 의미 한정. 핵의학 facility (cyclotron + radiopharmacy + γ-camera/PET-CT) physical infrastructure 필수가 본질적 한계.

